author.name: Prince Dr Nicholas C Ukachukwu MFR

profile_bio.description: Husband. Business man. Anambra State APC Governorship Candidate 2025

text:
ASIWAJU WELCOME TO IGBOLAND.
With utmost delight,we welcome His Excellency President Bola Ahmed Tinubu GCFR to Imo State ( Igboland)on a working visit.
Mr. President, your renewed hope agenda evident in your ingenious economic reforms are restoring investors confidence in our dear country.
In the same vein, your massive infrastructure development,youth empowerment and Social intervention programmes have increased citizens'trust and confidence in your administration.Congratulations Sir .
As a guest to the good people of Imo State( Igboland) and our leader His Excellency Senator Governor Hope Uzodimma - the  architect of a new, rising Imo who is  meticulously turning resources into results,we invite you to enjoy the inimitable Igbo hospitality.
Onye Isi ala Nnoo!
Yagazie.
